  <div class="dual-bars-wrap reveal" style="transition-delay:.15s" role="figure" aria-label="Stacked bar diagram showing 10 content domains. Bar height reflects how many states require that domain. The lower portion is the standard tier; the upper extension is the advanced tier built on the same base.">

